name: 水虎-Mizu Tora (Water Tiger)
description:
The water tiger once was an ordinary tiger that lived near a river or lake,
but after living for 500 years, it obtain a great power as a gift from god.
Posessed a power of god, he becomes a divine beast guardian of water elements,
reign all over aquatic terrain and creatures of water.
